aljalalyn_tafseer:
Indeed man was created restless: ( haluan is an implied circumstantial qualifier, the explanation 
of which [follows]): when evil befalls him, [he is] anxious, at the point of that evil befalling [him], and when good befalls him, [he is] grudging, at the point of that good befalling [him], that is to 
say, [when] wealth [befalls him], [he is grudging to give] of it what is due to God;
